high_descs: Turn around, go to the sink and then turn left
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the edge of the tub
Turn around then turn right and go to the toilet
Put the empty toilet paper roll on the lid of the toilet tank
anns.task_desc: Set the empty toilet paper roll on the top of the toilet tank lid

high_descs: walk over to the side of the tub basin
remove the toilet paper roll tube from the tub basin
take the empty tube and walk to the toilet
stand the empty tube up on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Take the empty toilet paper tube from the tub basin to the back of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around, proceed to center of tub.  Turn left to face tub.
Pick up cup from edge of tub.
Place cup on back of toilet between candle and pump bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move cup from tub edge to back of toilet.
